herings</p></li><li><p>Full-panel blood testing</p></li><li><p>4x guest passes per month </p></li><li><p>Access to exclusive merch</p></li></ul></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="727a4236-8671-4939-a01e-ce5aa6fb0503" class="r-1mze037" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="6eea269c-77fa-4f6c-884d-c66acf598d63" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Ref32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-cgxihl"><div data-rid="89b70782-ceef-47d9-86b6-60b4c5ffaca2" class="r-wqopya alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Are there in-person events?</p></span></div><div data-rid="71d2b183-f88e-4222-935f-6f54664d8296" class="r-1aplb44" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1r6vs2a" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:Ref32:"><div data-rid="2317c43d-c085-4415-a3ac-9d7b7b703d0b" class="r-1fz33yx"><div data-rid="9faddc62-cb7c-4e76-9c06-962b0f980cd3" class="r-yl7w3y alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Yes. In-person members have access to regular on-site events, including:</p><ul><li><p>Seasonal celebrations and community events</p></li><li><p>Member only wellness and social gatherings</p></li><li><p>Family-friendly days and festivals </p></li><li><p>Educational workshops and guest speakers</p></li></ul></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="dc4a6693-e9d3-4973-b825-b87cf4e38764" class="r-co9n27" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="adc07938-dea6-4a1b-930c-5bc91d3f5eee" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:Rif32:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1o7nb0p"><div data-r